      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ORANA REX (2) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 3.5 lengths over 300m this track in 17.71. Overdue and expected to feature again. BLUE CRACKER (1) produced a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 300m behind Incredible Lucky (17.79) in a Novice race. Form from his last run is proving strong. Expected to run well. IN HER PRIME (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 4 (17.46). Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Got the money at her only try from this box. Must be included in calculations. EMERGING (5) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
